                          RANGER'S GUILD HELP
----------------------------------------------------------------------------
GETTING STARTED:
  setprime <terrain>   Set your primary terrain (one-time, do first!)
  setsecond <terrain>  Set your secondary terrain (one-time)
  setenemy <race>      Set your enemy species (one-time)

SKILLS & ADVANCEMENT:
  skilltree / tree     View the full skill tree and your progress.
  learn                See skills available to learn.
  learn <skill>        Learn a new skill (costs slots).
  learn cost <skill>   See the cost and details of a skill.
  skills / myskills    Show your learned skills.
  slots                Show your available skill slots.
  improve <what>       Advance stats/level or review Ranger XP.
  cost / tally         Show character costs and Ranger XP.
  check <terrain>      See what skills work in a terrain.

INFORMATION:
  ranhelp / rh         Show this screen. 'rh <topic>' for details.
  rscore / rsc         Your Ranger status report.
  rangers              Show Rangers currently online.
  bio / myinfo         View or set your Ranger bio.
  motto / declare      Set your motto (shown on 'rangers' list).
  survey / id          Identify the terrain you are in.
  inspect <target>     Analyze an opponent's strengths.

COMMUNICATION:
  ran <message>        Chat on the Ranger guild line.
  eran <message>       Emote on the Ranger guild line.
  signal <who> <msg>   Send a nature-carried message to a player.

GUILD MANAGEMENT:
  recruit <name>       Recruit another player into the guild.
  rebuild quiver       Get a new quiver if yours is lost.
  repair quiver        Refresh your quiver if having problems.
  rangerbug <message>  Report a Ranger bug.
  journal              List available tasks and quests.

ADDITIONAL TOPICS:   general guildhall advancement skills glevels
                     terrains stats archery weapons armour emotes
                     followers enemy alignment history philosophy
                     conduct equipment powerlist

TERRAINS:            forest plains swamp desert jungle city hills sea
                     lake river road inside beach underground
                     mountain arctic barren underwater
